message.body: Are you guys heading back to Philly?? How'd it go this weekend??
We are back! Got in late last night. It was good! I'm kind of freakin' tho.
Why??
Hunter made an offer. Eyepatch
Yeeps!
Ahhhhh!! Are you serious?? What does this mean??
Did you love it there???

I thought asheville was kind of lame but the land and area is beautiful. I'm worried about work. There is someone else coming to look at the property on September 8th. Apparently they are really into it too
We have been talking about all the pros and cons
That is so wild! Let's talk more about this very soon...are you around this weekend to get dinner??
I'm busy Friday night but free Saturday or Sunday might!
Wanna do dinner at cantina Saturday night?
Perfect! I really need to talk through this. The house is sooo small.
Great! We will talk the shit outta this!
I'm guessing your cons list looked something like this: #1 move away from Tess...;)
Seriously. It was such a long drive and all the hippies in town made me angry!
I was so mad at the hippies.
Unreasonably
Sounds reasonable to me...hippies are infuriating...especially in abundance.
Can you do an earlier dinner on Saturday?? Maybe like 5ish?
Hey sure!
